Clopidogrel versus aspirin for secondary prophylaxis of vascular events: a 
cost-effectiveness analysis.

Schleinitz MD(1), Weiss JP, Owens DK.

Author information:
(1)Department of Medicine (JPW), Stanford University, Palo Alto, California, 
USA. Mark_Schleinitz@Brown.edu

